    <span style=3D"color:#A020F0">"int16=3D&gt;single"</span>,0,<span style=
=3D"color:#A020F0">"bsq"</span>,<span style=3D"color:#A020F0">"ieee-be"</sp=
an>);</pre></div></div></div><h3 class=3D"title" id=3D"VolumeRegistrationEx=
ample-2">Display Unregistered Images</h3><p>Judge the alignment of the unre=
gistered volumes by displaying the middle transverse slice of each volume u=
sing <a href=3D"https://ww2.mathworks.cn/help/releases/R2023b/images/ref/im=
showpair.html" data-docid=3D"images_ref#bta3ucy-1" class=3D"a"><code class=
=3D"olink">imshowpair</code></a>. The MRI slice is magenta, and the CT slic=
e is green. The scaling differences indicate that the images have different=
 pixel spacing.</p><div class=3D"code_responsive -has_code_copy"><div class=
=3D"programlisting"><div class=3D"codeinput"><div class=3D"btn-group code_a=
ctions"> <button type=3D"button" class=3D"btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" =
data-toggle=3D"dropdown" aria-haspopup=3D"true" aria-expanded=3D"false"> <s=
pan class=3D"copy_code_popover_target" id=3D"copy_popover_02"><span class=
=3D"icon-copy" id=3D"copy_popover_02"></span> Get <span class=3D"caret" id=
=3D"copy_popover_02"></span></span></button><ul class=3D"dropdown-menu drop=
down-menu-right copy_code"><li class=3D"copy_code_block"><button id=3D"copy=
Block02"><span class=3D"icon-copy"></span> Copy Code Block</button></li><li=
 role=3D"separator" aria-hidden=3D"true" class=3D"divider"></li><li class=
=3D"copy_code_openexample"><p><span class=3D"icon-webinar"></span> Copy ope=
