n></div></li></ul></div><pre>centerFixed =3D size(fixedVolume,3)/2;
centerMoving =3D size(movingVolume,3)/2;
figure
imshowpair(movingVolume(:,:,centerMoving),fixedVolume(:,:,centerFixed))
title(<span style=3D"color:#A020F0">"Unregistered Transverse Slice"</span>)=
</pre></div></div></div><div class=3D"informalfigure"><div id=3D"d126e18589=
" class=3D"mediaobject"><p><img src=3D"https://ww2.mathworks.cn/help/releas=
es/R2023b/examples/images/win64/VolumeRegistrationExample_01.png" width=3D"=
678"></p></div></div><p>You can also display the volumes as 3-D objects. Cr=
eate a <code class=3D"literal">viewer3d</code> object, in which you can dis=
play multiple volumes.</p><div class=3D"code_responsive -has_code_copy"><di=
v class=3D"programlisting"><div class=3D"codeinput"><div class=3D"btn-group=
 code_actions"> <button type=3D"button" class=3D"btn btn-default dropdown-t=
oggle" data-toggle=3D"dropdown" aria-haspopup=3D"true" aria-expanded=3D"fal=
se"> <span class=3D"copy_code_popover_target" id=3D"copy_popover_03"><span =
class=3D"icon-copy" id=3D"copy_popover_03"></span> Get <span class=3D"caret=
" id=3D"copy_popover_03"></span></span></button><ul class=3D"dropdown-menu =
dropdown-menu-right copy_code"><li class=3D"copy_code_block"><button id=3D"=
copyBlock03"><span class=3D"icon-copy"></span> Copy Code Block</button></li=
><li role=3D"separator" aria-hidden=3D"true" class=3D"divider"></li><li cla=
ss=3D"copy_code_openexample"><p><span class=3D"icon-webinar"></span> Copy o=
penExample Command<br><small>Paste command in MATLAB to download and open e=
xample files</small></p><div role=3D"presentation" class=3D"input-group"><i=
nput type=3D"text" class=3D"form-control" readonly=3D"" value=3D"openExampl=
e('images/VolumeRegistrationExample')"><span class=3D"input-group-btn"><but=
ton class=3D"btn btn_color_blue" type=3D"button" id=3D"copyCommand03"><span=
 class=3D"icon-copy"><span class=3D"sr-only">Copy</span></span></button></s=
pan></div></li></ul></div><pre>viewerUnregistered =3D viewer3d(BackgroundCo=
lor=3D<span style=3D"color:#A020F0">"black"</span>,BackgroundGradient=3D<sp=
an style=3D"color:#A020F0">"off"</span>);</pre></div></div></div><p>Display=
 the <code class=3D"literal">medicalVolume</code> objects as 3-D isosurface=
s by using the <a href=3D"https://ww2.mathworks.cn/help/releases/R2023b/ima=
ges/ref/volshow.html" data-docid=3D"images_ref#mw_a016c22f-b57a-4eb8-922b-9=
6f2a2056fc3" class=3D"a"><code class=3D"olink">volshow</code></a> function.=
 You can rotate the volumes by clicking and dragging in the viewer window. =
When you plot the 3-D isosurfaces in intrinsic coordinates, they appear ver=
tically distorted because the slice thickness is different than the in-plan=
e pixel spacing in world coordinates.</p><div class=3D"code_responsive -has=
_code_copy"><div class=3D"programlisting"><div class=3D"codeinput"><div cla=
ss=3D"btn-group code_actions"> <button type=3D"button" class=3D"btn btn-def=
ault dropdown-toggle" data-toggle=3D"dropdown" aria-haspopup=3D"true" aria-=
expanded=3D"false"> <span class=3D"copy_code_popover_target" id=3D"copy_pop=
over_04"><span class=3D"icon-copy" id=3D"copy_popover_04"></span> Get <span=
 class=3D"caret" id=3D"copy_popover_04"></span></span></button><ul class=3D=
"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right copy_code"><li class=3D"copy_code_block"=
><button id=3D"copyBlock04"><span class=3D"icon-copy"></span> Copy Code Blo=
ck</button></li><li role=3D"separator" aria-hidden=3D"true" class=3D"divide=
r"></li><li class=3D"copy_code_openexample"><p><span class=3D"icon-webinar"=
></span> Copy openExample Command<br><small>Paste command in MATLAB to down=
load and open example files</small></p><div role=3D"presentation" class=3D"=
input-group"><input type=3D"text" class=3D"form-control" readonly=3D"" valu=
e=3D"openExample('images/VolumeRegistrationExample')"><span class=3D"input-=
group-btn"><button class=3D"btn btn_color_blue" type=3D"button" id=3D"copyC=
ommand04"><span class=3D"icon-copy"><span class=3D"sr-only">Copy</span></sp=
an></button></span></div></li></ul></div><pre>volshow(fixedVolume,Parent=3D=
viewerUnregistered,RenderingStyle=3D<span style=3D"color:#A020F0">"Isosurfa=
ce"</span>, <span style=3D"color:#0000FF">...</span>
    Colormap=3D[1 0 1],Alphamap=3D1);
